@node "PLUG!" "EmBackdrops - The Shameless Plug!"
       _     _   _
      (_    (   (_|_
Other (_/\/\_)()| (_ Programs
-----------------------------

The Paper Counter
The ultimate in paper counting technology on your Amiga.
Should be available on the Aminet as 'PaperCounter.lha' under 'util/misc'

EmSpool - The Frame-by-Frame Hard Disk ANIM 5 spooler.
CLI Animation spooler. (for Anims in DPaint etc. format)
Should be available on the Aminet as 'EmSpool.lha' under 'gfx/show'

Both are freely distributable and should be available from any PD library.
If you can't find them they are both available directly from me.  Just send
an SAE and a blank disk to the address @{"elsewhere in the documentation" link "AUTHOR"}.

EmBackdrops 1 is also available in 'pix/mwb' as 'EmBackdrops.lha'.


